{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.125\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">上行之詩。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">耶和華子民的安全</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.125.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>倚靠耶和華的人好像<span class=\"pn\">錫安山</span>，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">安穩坐鎮，永不動搖。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.125.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>眾山怎樣圍繞<span class=\"pn\">耶路撒冷</span>，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">耶和華也照樣圍繞他的百姓，從今時直到永遠。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.125.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>惡人的杖必不在義人的土地上停留，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">免得義人伸手作惡。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.125.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>耶和華啊，求你善待</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">行善和心裏正直的人。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.125.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>至於那偏行彎曲道路的人，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">耶和華必將他們和作惡的人一同驅逐出去。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\">願平安歸於<span class=\"pn\">以色列</span>！</span></p>\n</div>\n"}